  "texts": [
    "By generating diverse, realistic 3D content and interaction scenarios, Generative AI can strengthen AR systems' performance and reliability, allowing more efficient training and immersive surgical experience.",
    "Exam preparationMultiple-choice question (MCQs) tests are common in medical education, and students frequently rely on various question bank resources for thorough answer explanations.",
    "Generative AI tools could significantly enhance this process by serving as virtual teaching assistants.",
    "They can provide specific insights into each MCQ and offer targeted feedback on challenging concepts leading to a better understanding of key topics and better exam preparation.",
    "Generative AI tools can also be used to produce customized MCQs based on specific topics and difficulty levels, adapting to the user's progress and reinforcing key concepts [67][68][69]."
  ]
}